Illicit financial crime like bribery, internet fraud and tax avoidance is not victimless. We all suffer. This is because, money lost to illicit financial crime could be used to build our roads, create a class health and education system and create jobs for Nigerians. Watch the video below to find out more, then join others in your community in standing up to Illicit Financial Crime by reporting all suspicious transactions to relevant authorities. #protectwhatsyours  This is part of a sensitisation campaign against illicit financial crime.